{"product_id":"honeysticks-bath-crayon-triangles-10pk","title":"Honeysticks Bath Crayons Triangles 10pk","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"SCXW222297252 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW222297252 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"p1\"\u003eTriangular crayons for tub-time creativity. \u003cstrong\u003eHoneysticks Bath Crayon Triangles 10pk\u003c\/strong\u003e are the perfect first step into bath-time art. With their clever triangle shape, they’re easy to grip, won’t roll away, and are made with pure beeswax and soy wax for safe, sensory play.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul class=\"ul1\"\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"li1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan class=\"s1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cb\u003eShaped for small hands:\u003c\/b\u003e The triangle design encourages grip development and early mark-making – perfect for little artists just getting started. Plus, it won’t roll off the tub mid-play. When they’re ready for the next stage, try our Honeysticks Bath Crayon Super Jumbos.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"li1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan class=\"s1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cb\u003eCreative confidence, built in the bath:\u003c\/b\u003e Support sensory learning, coordination and imagination, all while making a splash.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"li1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan class=\"s1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cb\u003eTen vibrant colours to explore:\u003c\/b\u003e For drawing, doodling, and colour-filled fun that washes off when the fun is done.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"li1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan class=\"s1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cb\u003eNo nasties, just pure creativity:\u003c\/b\u003e Crafted with natural beeswax and soy wax, plus food-grade colourants. Safe for play, safe for planet.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"li1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan class=\"s1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cb\u003eWipes clean with warm water:\u003c\/b\u003e No scrubbing needed – a gentle wipe and the tub is ready for next time.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"li1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan class=\"s1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cb\u003eLovingly handmade in New Zealand:\u003c\/b\u003e Created by parents who believe in a better way to play – safe, sustainable, and designed to inspire from the very first splash.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"p1\"\u003e\u003cem\u003e\u003cb\u003eNow in our refreshed Honeysticks look – welcome to a world of pure creation!\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Honeysticks UK","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":56350550262141,"sku":"HBTTR10","price":17.95,"currency_code":"GBP","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0553\/5465\/4896\/files\/Bath-Crayons2_2dcc4a48-2928-4de6-b1e9-d88a11b86876.png?v=1765336282","url":"https:\/\/honeysticks.co.uk\/products\/honeysticks-bath-crayon-triangles-10pk","provider":"Honeysticks UK","version":"1.0","type":"link"}